name: Closet Deadhead Grateful Dead Gifts, Inc.
overview: Closet DeadHead, Inc. is your ultimate source of everything that is Grateful Dead. Our site is loaded with Grateful Dead memorabilia and collectibles you probably still don’t have in possession. From vintage albums since the band’s early beginnings to the latest concert recordings of the remaining members, you can find them right here. We also have the coolest Grateful Dead gears like t-shirts, sweatshirts, underwear, belt buckles, shoes, jewelry, and other accessories, even baby clothes. We offer a wide selection of collectibles such as glasses and mugs, key chains, bags, bandannas, tapestries, blankets, posters, buttons, patches, toys and games, and a whole lot more! We keep the Grateful Dead very much alive here at ClosetDeadHead.com.
